      <title>肯尼亚议员希望总统任期延长至七年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/kenyan-lawmakers-want-president-s-term-extended-to-seven-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《每日民族报》报道，肯尼亚议员提议修改宪法，将总统和议会任期从五年延长至七年。]]></description>
